title: #92Noon! Baldy/Eskin/Florio/Ard/Sirles!
description: NFL Network's Brian Baldinger starts an hour of Vikes/Eagles with Philly's Howard Eskin & then Florio to finish. Super Bowl Stories with Bill Ard, final hour is all Vikings OL Jeremiah Sirles, and an updated version of the "Hunger" cover is in as well!
